data.description: Introducing a magnificent 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms home, nestled in the gorgeous community of Sacramento. Built in 2018 and looks brand new. This stunning abode boasts a graceful and sleek design, with meticulous attention to detail with an open concept. The spacious living area is perfect for hosting family and friends, with plenty of natural light flooding in through the numerous windows. The gourmet kitchen features granite countertops and ample cabinet space. The luxurious owner's suite boasts a spa-like bathroom and a large walk-in closet, and the additional bedrooms are generously-sized and have plenty of closet space. The second floor has a loft with space for a media/office area perfect for relaxing and entertaining. With easy access to top-rated schools, shopping, and fine dining, this home is the epitome of upscale living. Refrigerator, washer and dryer do not convey. This GEM won't last long. SOLD AS IS.
